  <h2>12. Limitation of Liability</h2>
  <p>To the maximum extent permitted by UK law, The Wish Wall shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, or consequential loss arising from use of the Platform. Our total liability shall not exceed the amount you paid to use the Platform.</p>

  <h2>13. Fraud &amp; Legal Action</h2>
  <p>Any attempt to obtain grants through deception constitutes fraud. For the purposes of the Computer Misuse Act 1990, Fraud Act 2006 (UK), and equivalent statutes globally, fraudulent submissions may result in account suspension, recovery of disbursed funds, and referral to law enforcement.</p>

